<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Setup Complete - AI Concierge</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .success-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #198754;
    }
    .success-card {
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .next-steps-title {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
        <div class="card success-card">
          <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
            <svg class="success-icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
              <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
            </svg>
            
            <h1 class="app-title mb-3">Activation Complete!</h1>
            
            <p class="lead mb-4">
              Your calendar is now connected to the AI Concierge. Client appointments will automatically appear in your selected calendar.
            </p>
            
            <div class="alert alert-success mb-4">
              <p class="mb-0">
                <strong>You're all set!</strong> Your account has been activated successfully.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps text-start">
              <h4 class="next-steps-title">Next Steps:</h4>
              <ol class="ps-3">
                <li class="mb-2">Check your email for additional setup instructions</li>
                <li class="mb-2">You can respond to your clients' messages as usual</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Appointments will be automatically added to your Google Calendar</li>
                <li>Our AI assistant will handle scheduling conflicts and client confirmations</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-muted mt-4 mb-0">
              Thank you for choosing AI Concierge for your scheduling needs!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>